QUERY (\triple total -> if tripleContainsString triple (Just "Renaud_de_Cormont") Nothing Nothing then addTriple total triple else total)
FROM personGraph
TO rdf
RETURN all

QUERY (\x newrdf -> if length (triplesOf newrdf) < 5 then addTriple newrdf x else newrdf)
FROM personGraph
TO rdf
RETURN all
